{
  "stem": "13817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[DRINKS] The ambulance itself was with a big red cross, a [? white ?] [? deal. ?] And the people would be laid in there about 10 to 12 people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then you would close the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And at the same time, they would hook the-- the hose from the exhaust right to-- into a special connection to that box, that red cross box.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Would drive around for an hour, and then people all would be dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So this was one way of taking care of the-- of the sick people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We-- all we-- everybody had diarrhea, more or less.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody got sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you-- you were afraid to stay home because they would bring you to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you went to work, sick or not sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had some doctors there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They told us-- what we did, for instance, for diarrhea-- the medication we-- we had, we would take wood and would burn it to ashes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the ashes itselves would be-- would make-- we would take the-- eat the ashes as a-- as a medication.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So supposedly, the-- the medication for-- for diarrhea is part of-- of ashes or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had some doctors there what told us to do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it usually helped, to a certain extent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, this camp, like I said before, at night, you had a big, like a [NON-ENGLISH] in your room where you could to release yourselves, to urinate only.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other one-- the-- the whole area was lit up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to walk to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the latrine was quite to the side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you could avoid it, you wouldn't go because it was so cold during the nighttime.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
